(60, 'B GD&T tr li 9 vn  c tri quan tm', 'b-gdat-tr-li-9-vn--c-tri-quan-tam', '', '<div class="subtitle">\r\n	B GD&T tr li cht vn ti k hp th 2, Quc hi kha XIII:</div>\r\n<div class="title" id="detail-title">\r\n	B GD&T tr li 9 vn  c tri quan tm</div>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">\r\n	(GD&T)-Thc hin yu cu ti Cng vn s 8273/VPCP-TH ngy 21/11/2011 ca Vn phng Chnh ph v vic phn cng cc thnh vin Chnh ph tr li cht vn ti Hi trng, B GD&T tr li cc vn  lin quan n lnh vc gio dc v o to.</p>\r\n<table align="center" cellpadding="3" cellspacing="0" class="image center" width="500">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n				<img alt="x Na C Sa, huyn Mng Nh, tnh in Bin" height="375" src="http://www.gdtd.vn/dataimages/201111/original/images598657_555.jpg" width="500" /></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td align="center" class="image_desc">\r\n				<span style="font-size: x-small;">Cc em hc sinh  x Na C Sa, huyn Mng Nh, tnh in Bin bn "T sch ca em"<br />\r\n				</span></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">\r\n	<strong>1. Cht lng gio dc ph thng</strong><br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	T nm hc 2006-2007, B Gio dc v o to trin khai thc hin Ch th s 33/2006/CT-TTg ngy 08/9/2006 ca Th tng Chnh ph v chng tiu cc v khc phc bnh thnh tch trong gio dc, thng qua cuc vn ng &ldquo;Hai khng&rdquo; ca ngnh,  to ra nhng c gng ci thin cht lng dy hc, gp phn quan trng tng bc nng cao cht lng gio dc.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	B Gio dc v o to ch o cc a phng, cc c s gio dc ch trng cc gii php: gio dc  thc hc thc cht v tng lai ca mnh v trch nhim vi x hi; h tr hc sinh yu t u nm hc, u cp hc; vn ng 3 ; i mi phng php dy hc, i mi phng php kim tra, nh gi; hng dn dy hc theo chun kin thc k nng; hon thin c s vt cht; Tng cng cng tc bi dng nng cao nng lc cho nh gio v hiu trng cc trng ph thng; Tham mu  cp y, chnh quyn cc a phng c s ch o st sao c h thng chnh tr  a phng chung tay vi ngnh chm lo cho gio dc.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	Cng vi vic ch o cc a phng thc hin nhiu gii php nh trn, thi gian va qua B Gio dc v o to  t chc mt s hi ngh chuyn ngnh nh: Hi ngh v hng dn bin son v ging dy lch s a phng; Hi tho qun l i mi phng php dy hc dy hc; Hi ngh kim tra nh gi thc y i mi phng php dy hc... Bn cnh , B Gio dc v o to cng  ban hnh hng dn dy hc theo chun kin thc &ndash; k nng; Hng dn quy trnh bin son  kim tra; Hng nm t chc bi dng, tp hun cho gio vin v tng cng r sot ni dung dy hc nhm iu chnh cc vn  bt hp l trong chng trnh sch gio khoa. Bn cnh , B thng xuyn tin hnh kim tra, n c vic trin khai thc hin nhim v nm hc, vic thc hin cc ni dung chuyn mn ca cc mn hc. Phong tro thi ua xy dng &ldquo;Trng hc thn thin, hc sinh tch cc&rdquo; cng c tc ng rt tch cc v i mi phng php dy hc, gn dy hc l thuyt vi thc hnh, l lun vi thc tin&hellip;<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	Vi s ch o quyt lit B Gio dc v o to, s ng h ca cc cp y ng, chnh quyn v nhn dn, cng vi s n lc c gng ca cc cp qun l gio dc, gio vin v  thc vn ln trong hc tp ca cc em hc sinh, cht lng gio dc  c tng bc nng ln, kt qu tt nghip trung hc ph thng  thay i theo chiu hng tch cc, phn nh ng cht lng gio dc. Cht lng  &lsquo;&lsquo;vng trng&rsquo;&rsquo;,  khu vc hc sinh yu km  chuyn bin tch cc, c th nh sau: T l tt nghip trong k thi nm 2007 ch t 66,7%; nm 2008: 76,0%, tng hn 9% so vi nm 2007; nm 2009: 83,8%, tng 7,8% so vi nm 2008; nm 2010: 92,57%, tng 8,97% so vi nm 2009; nm 2011: 95,72%, tng 3,15% so vi nm 2010. Trong , s th sinh tt nghip loi trung bnh chim a s (86,17%), ch c 13,83% t loi kh gii v t l th sinh c im bnh qun bi thi t trung bnh tr ln ch t 81,36%.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	Nhng ch s trn cho thy s c gng nhng nm qua nhm nng cao kt qu hc tp ca hc sinh mi ch yu t c nh nng cht lng hc sinh hc t hc lc yu, km ln mc trung bnh, cha nng c nhiu cht lng hc sinh kh gii.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	Xc nh r trch nhim ca mnh, B Gio dc v o to  v ang tng cng ch o ton ngnh y mnh vic i mi phng php dy hc, kim tra nh gi, khuyn khch cc nh trng i mi phng php dy hc tch cc v hiu qu ph hp vi vng min; to ra s chuyn bin r rt v cht lng dy hc trong ton ngnh.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	Trc mt, B  hng dn thc hin c hiu qu vic iu chnh nhng bt hp l trong chng trnh, SGK theo hng tinh gim ni dung, dnh nhiu c hi cho gio vin c ch ng, sng to trong qu trnh dy hc; khc phc li dy hc thun tu c - chp; bo m cn i gia vic truyn th kin thc v rn luyn k nng cho hc sinh; ch trng lin h thc t ph hp vi ni dung bi hc; ch trng t chc cho hc sinh lm vic c nhn v theo nhm hp l; rn luyn k nng t hc, to iu kin cho hc sinh t nghin cu sch gio khoa v ti liu tham kho; xy dng h thng cu hi hp l, ph hp vi cc i tng, tp trung vo trng tm, trnh nng n qu ti; bi dng nng lc c lp suy ngh, vn dng sng to kin thc  hc. Tng cng t chc cc hot ng ngoi kha, hot ng gio dc ngoi gi ln lp nhm m bo tnh linh hot v hnh thc dy hc, hnh thc kim tra, nh gi, rn luyn k nng sng v k nng hot ng x hi ca hc sinh. Khuyn khch, ng vin, khen thng kp<br />\r\n	thi nhng gio vin gii, hc sinh gii i i vi vic gip , ph o cc hc sinh yu, hc sinh c hon cnh kh khn; T chc c hiu qu vic n tp  hc sinh nm vng ni dung kin thc v phng php hc tp, lm bi.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	Bn cnh , B tch cc ch o i mi vic kim tra, nh gi c trong kim tra thng xuyn, kim tra nh k cng nh thi tt nghip THPT v tuyn sinh i hc, cao ng theo hng: Gim yu cu phi nh my mc; tng yu cu thng hiu, vn dng kin thc v k nng.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	Cng vi nhng gii php cp bch , v lu di, B Gio dc v o to s nghin cu v tin hnh i mi chng trnh, sch gio khoa, i mi phng php v hnh thc dy hc, kim tra nh gi theo nh hng bi dng nng lc v thi , tnh cm m hc sinh t c sau khi hc tp; Tng cng cc iu kin dy hc, phi hp xy dng mi trng x hi thun li cho vic dy hc.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	<strong>2. V quy hoch mng li, thnh lp, nng cp cc trng i hc, cao ng</strong><br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	Trong hn 10 nm qua, h thng gio dc i hc  tng bc pht trin v loi hnh trng v hnh thc o to, cung cp ngun lao ng c trnh  cao ng, i hc, sau i hc phc v tch cc cho s nghip pht trin kinh t - x hi, quc phong - an ninh. n nay, c nc c 202 trng i hc, 218 trng cao ng (bao gm cc trng thnh vin trc thuc cc i hc Quc gia, i hc Vng, khng k cc trng i hc, cao ng thuc khi Quc phng - An ninh).<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	Vic thnh lp, nng cp cc trng i hc, cao ng nhn chung ph hp vi trin khai Quy hoch mng li cc trng i hc, cao ng  c Th tng Chnh ph ph duyt (Quyt nh s 121/2007/Q-TTg ngy 27/7/2007), ph hp vi nh hng, mc tiu pht trin kinh t - x hi ca tng vng, tng a phng; ph hp vi ch trng ca ng, nh nc v khuyn khch x hi ha gio dc, khuyn khch cc nh u t c nng lc v ti chnh, tm huyt vi s nghip gio dc u t xy dng cc trng i hc, cao ng ngoi cng lp v c da trn nhng cn c ch yu sau y:<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	- Lut Gio dc nm 2005; Ngh nh s 75/2006/N-CP ngy 2-8-2006 ca Chnh ph v Quy nh chi tit v hng dn thi hnh mt s iu ca Lut Gio dc;<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	- Cc Ngh quyt ca ng v pht trin kinh t-x hi v m bo an ninh quc phng thi k 2001-2010 cc vng: Ty Nguyn; ng bng sng Cu long; Vng trung du v min ni Bc b; Bc trung b v duyn hi trung b; ng bng sng Hng; ng Nam b v vng kinh t trng im pha nam;<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	- Cc Quyt nh ca Th tng Chnh ph v phng hng ch yu pht trin kinh t-x hi n nm 2010 v tm nhn n nm 2020 cc vng: Vng kinh t trng im Bc b; vng kinh t trng im min trung; Vng kinh t trng im pha nam; Vng ng bng sng Cu long;<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	- Ti liu hng dn ca B K hoch v u t v ni dung, phng php nghin cu lp quy hoch tng th pht trin kinh t-x hi thi k 2005-2020 ca B K hoch v u t;<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	- Cc Quy hoch tng th pht trin kinh t-x hi tng khu vc, tng vng kinh t trng im, tng a phng, mt s quy hoch chuyn ngnh ca cc B, ngnh  c Th tng Chnh ph ph duyt;<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	Tiu ch  xem xt cc iu kin thnh lp trng i hc c cn c vo Quyt nh s 07/2009/Q-TTg ngy 15/01/2009 ca Th tng Chnh ph v iu kin v th tc thnh lp, chia, tch, sp nhp trng i hc.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	Trong 6 nm qua (2006-2011),  thnh lp 84 trng i hc mi, trong  51 trng nng cp t trng cao ng v 33 trng thnh lp mi, bnh qun mi nm thnh lp 14 trng. C th: 3 nm u (t nm 2006 n nm 2008)  thnh lp mi 24 trng v nng cp 25 trng, bnh qun mi nm thnh lp 16 trng. T nm 2009 n thng 7/2011, c 26 trng cao ng nng cp thnh i hc v 09 trng i hc thnh lp mi, bnh qun mi nm thnh lp 12 trng. Nh vy, s lng trng i hc thnh lp mi trong 3 nm gn y  gim nhiu so vi trc v ch yu l nng cp t cc trng cng lp.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	Cc iu kin thnh lp trng v cho php trng i hc hot ng cng  c iu chnh theo hng nng cao, v d, sau khi cc trng c thnh lp, nu m bo cc iu kin, tiu ch v c s vt cht, trang thit b, s lng v cht lng i ng ging vin chuyn ngnh theo quy nh th B Gio dc v o to mi cho php hot ng o to, m ngnh v tuyn sinh. Cn nu trng c php thnh lp nhng cha chun b y  cc iu kin, B Gio dc v o to khng cho php hot ng o to v tuyn sinh, trnh tnh trng cc trng va c thnh lp c php trin khai hot ng o to ngay khi cha p ng  cc iu kin, dn n o to cht lng km.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	Trn c s xem xt cc iu kin v nng lc o to ca nh trng (chng trnh o to, c s vt cht, i ng ging vin, cn b qun l) v  xut ch tiu tuyn sinh ca c s o to, B Gio dc v o to cn c vo quy hoch pht trin ngun nhn lc chung ca c nc  giao ch tiu tuyn sinh cho tng c s o to.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	Trong hai nm qua, B Gio dc v o to :<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	a) Tng bc gim nhp  thnh lp trng (nm 2007 thnh lp mi 10 trng i hc, 6 trng cao ng; nm 2008 thnh lp mi 8 trng i hc, 7 trng cao ng; nm 2009 thnh lp mi 4 trng i hc, 1 trng cao ng; nm 2010 thnh lp mi 4 trng i hc, 1 trng cao ng; nm 2011 thnh lp mi 01 trng i hc).<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	b) Gim ch tiu tuyn sinh khng chnh quy (nm 2010, gim 20% v nm 2011 gim 40% so vi tng ch tiu tuyn sinh chnh quy).<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	c) Tm dng vic m ngnh, chuyn ngnh o to cao ng, i hc, thc s, tin s ca cc c s o to  xy dng quy trnh mi.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	d) Tm ngng tuyn sinh 101 chuyn ngnh o to trnh  tin s  cc trng khng  iu kin m bo cht lng o to.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	e) Tm ngng tuyn sinh i hc h chnh quy nm 2010 ca trng i hc Cng ngh ng  v trng i hc Phan Chu Trinh.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	 tng bc nng cao cht lng o to, B Gio dc v o to  v ang tin hnh mt s gii php nh sau:<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	a) R sot, iu chnh quy hoch mng li trng i hc, cao ng trn phm vi c nc.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	b) Tip tc i mi qun l gio dc i hc, y mnh phn cp, giao quyn t ch, t chu trch nhim cho c s gio dc i hc.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	c) Xy dng v nng cao cht lng i ng ging vin v cn b qun l gio dc i hc.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	d) n nh ch tiu tuyn sinh chnh quy, tip tc gim ch tiu tuyn sinh khng chnh quy.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	) Tng cng cng tc kim nh cht lng gio dc i hc.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	e) y mnh o to theo nhu cu x hi, gn o to vi nghin cu khoa hc, gia cc c s o to vi cc doanh nghip.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	g) Tng cng cng tc thanh tra, kim tra iu kin m bo cht lng v thc hin cam kt thnh lp trng; x l nghim tc cc trng vi phm.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	<strong> 3. V cht lng tuyn sinh i hc<br />\r\n	</strong><br />\r\n	Trn c s s liu thng k chnh thc kt qu tuyn sinh ca nm 2010 l 510.000 sinh vin h i hc, cao ng, B Gio dc v o to  xc nh k hoch tuyn sinh ca nm 2011 l 543.000 ch tiu, tng 6,47%.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	Trn c s kt qu thi i hc ton quc, ch tiu tuyn sinh v chnh sch u tin theo i tng v khu vc, Hi ng im sn quc gia  xc nh im sn xt tuyn i hc nm 2011 i vi hc sinh ph thng  khu vc 3 l 13,0 im (khi A, D) v 14,0 im (khi B, C) (gi nguyn im sn nh nm 2010).<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	Nu mt trng i hc xc nh im trng tuyn bng im sn th  trng tuyn, kt qu thi ca th sinh l hc sinh ph thng  khu vc 3 (cc thnh ph trc thuc Trung ng) phi t ti thiu 13 im/3 mn thi (i vi th sinh d thi khi A v D), 14 im/3 mn thi (i vi th sinh d thi khi B v C) v khng c mn thi no b im 0. Nu 1 hc sinh  vng iu kin kh khn v c hng  mi ch  u tin (dn tc, a bn kh khn, con thng binh, lit s...) th phi t 8,0 im mi vo c trng i hc.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	Hin nay, mt s trng i hc, cao ng (c cng lp v ngoi cng lp) tuyn sinh khng  ch tiu c giao, do nhiu nguyn nhn khc nhau:<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	- Mt s ngnh cn o to (nng nghip, khoa hc c bn, s phm, khoa hc x hi, nhn vn...), do sau tt nghip cng vic khng hp dn, kh xin vic lm nn khng thu ht c sinh vin vo hc.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	- Mt s trng khng  iu kin m bo cht lng o to (c s vt cht i thu mn cht chi, i ng ging vin thiu nhiu, ch yu thnh ging) do vy khng thu ht c hc sinh vo hc.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	- Nhiu trng c ngnh o to ging nhau (nh K ton, Ti chnh - ngn hng, Qun tr kinh doanh nn chia x s lng sinh vin vo cc trng ny.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	Mc d mt s trng i hc kin ngh h im sn xt tuyn  tuyn  ch tiu  xc nh, nhng B Gio dc v o to khng chp thun ni lng u vo, khng v mc tiu chy theo s lng, m kin tr gi im sn xt tuyn,  bo m chun cht lng tuyn chn ti thiu ca cc trng i hc, gp phn nng cao cht lng o to.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	Qua thanh tra, kim tra cng tc tuyn sinh trong k tuyn sinh nm nay, n thi im ny, B Gio dc v o to cha pht hin trng i hc no h im chun xt tuyn th sinh c kt qu thi qu thp vo hc i hc.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	 nng cao cht lng o to, p ng nhu cu nhn lc cho pht trin t nc, B Gio dc v o to tip tc thc hin cc gii php sau:<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	- Xem xt nh gi li kt qu, hiu qu ca vic m trng trong giai on 2001-2010   xut, kin ngh vi Th tng Chnh ph sa i, iu chnh mt s mc tiu, ch tiu (v quy m sinh vin/vn dn, quy m bnh qun ca trng i hc, cao ng; t l sinh vin/ging vin theo nhm ngnh,...), ph hp Quy hoch pht trin ngun nhn lc Vit Nam giai on 2011-2020 theo nh hng quy hoch v pht trin kinh t - x hi, p ng nhu cu nhn lc ca cc a phng.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	- Tip tc ch o thc hin Ch th s 296/CT-TTg ngy 27/2/2010 ca Th tng Chnh ph v i mi qun l gio dc i hc giai on 2010-2012.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	- Tng cng cng tc kim nh cht lng trng i hc, cao ng; cng tc thanh tra, kim tra iu kin m bo cht lng o to ca cc trng theo Ngh quyt s 50/2010/QH12 ngy 19/6/2010 ca Quc hi kha XII v vic thc hin chnh sch, php lut v thnh lp trng, u t v m bo cht lng o to i vi gio dc i hc.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	- Thc hin vic xc nh ch tiu tuyn sinh ca mi trng theo cc quy nh ti Quyt nh s 795/Q-BGDT ngy 27/02/2010, trong  ch cn c vo ging vin c hu, khng tnh ging vin thnh ging; C l trnh iu chnh ch tiu tuyn sinh ca cc c s o to theo cc tiu ch  cng b.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	- Hon thin d tho Lut gio dc i hc  trnh Quc hi thng qua, to hnh lang php l vng chc cho cc c s gio dc i hc iu chnh cc hot ng v pht trin bn vng.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	B Gio dc v o to s nghin cu,  xut cc chnh sch khuyn khch, thu ht i vi ngi hc v sau khi tt nghip nhng ngnh ngh m nhu cu x hi cn, nhng khng thu ht c hc sinh, iu chnh quy m tuyn sinh v c cu ngnh ngh ph hp vi quy hoch ngun nhn lc i vi nhng ngnh, ngh c xu hng bo ha, tha trong tng lai.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	Trong cng tc ch o, B Gio dc v o to s tip tc quan tm, ch trng n cht lng v nng cao cht lng o to, xem y l mc tiu xuyn sut trong qu trnh i mi gio dc i hc.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	<strong>4. V lin kt o to thc s, tin s </strong><br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	Lin kt o to vi nc ngoi l mt trong nhng giai phap quan trng, gp phn nng cao cht lng gio dc i hc Vit Nam, a gio dc Vit Nam nhanh chng hi nhp vi gio dc quc t v khu vc khi Vit Nam  gia nhp WTO va hi nhp quc t ngy cng su rng.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	n nay, c 364 chng trnh lin kt o to vi nc ngoi ang c trin khai ti 63 c s o to do B Giao duc va ao tao v 05 i hc cp php. Cc chng trnh lin kt ny u c thm nh k cc iu kin theo quy nh.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	Tuy nhin, mt s vin, trung tm v mt s c s khc khng c chc nng o to, khng p ng cc iu kin quy nh vn t chc lin kt o to vi nc ngoi tri php,  gy bc xc trong d lun x hi v thit thi i vi ngi hc.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	Trong hai nm 2010 v 2011, B Giao duc va ao tao  tin hnh thanh tra, kim tra 27 c s gio dc i hc, mt s vin, trung tm c lin kt o to vi nc ngoi,  pht hin v c vn bn yu cu mt s c s chn chnh cc sai phm, lp h s xin php lin kt o to theo ng quy nh; nh ch hot ng ca mt s chng trnh lin kt o to cha c cp php.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	 m bo cht lng o to ca cc chng trnh lin kt, bo v quyn li ca ngi hc, B Giao duc va ao tao  ban hnh Quyt nh s 77/2007/Q-BGDT ngy 20/12/2007 quy nh v trnh t, th tc cng nhn vn bng ca ngi Vit Nam do c s gio dc nc ngoi cp.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	Trong thi gian ti,  quan ly cht che cac chng trinh lin kt o to vi nc ngoai, B Gio dc v o to trin khai mt s gii php sau:<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	a) Tip tc k cng nhn tng ng vn bng vi cc nc trong khu vc v trn th gii.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	b) Tip tc tng cng cng tc thanh tra, kim tra v x pht nghim cc vi phm v lin kt o to vi nc ngoi.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	c) Tng cng cng tc ch o v phi hp vi cc b, ngnh, a phng trong cng tc qun l hot ng lin kt o to vi nc ngoi v qun l nh nc v gio dc v o to theo Ngh nh 115/2010/N-CP ngy 24/12/2010 ca Chnh ph.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	d) Cng khai danh sch cc chng trnh lin kt o to vi nc ngoi c cp php trn website ca B Gio dc v o to.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	e) T chc Hi ngh v lin kt o to vi nc ngoi  tng kt, rt kinh nghim 10 nm thc hin lin kt o to vi nc ngoi ti Vit Nam.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	g) Trnh Chnh ph ban hnh Ngh nh mi v hp tc u t ca nc ngoi trong lnh vc gio dc v o to ti Vit Nam  m bo quy nh thng nht v cht ch v cc iu kin lin kt o to vi nc ngoi.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	<strong>5. Vn  &ldquo;chy trng&rdquo;</strong><br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	a) Thc trng tnh hnh: Thi gian va qua, bo ch c nu hin tng &ldquo;chy trng&rdquo;, &ldquo;chy lp&rdquo;  mt s  th ln. y khng phi tnh trng ph bin  nhiu a phng nhng  gy bc xc trong d lun x hi.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	b) Nguyn nhn<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	- Cht lng dch v v gio dc gia cc c s gio dc mm non v ph thng trn a bn trong mt qun, huyn, th x, thnh ph khng ng u, trong kh  tm l cha m hc sinh mun con hc trng c nhiu dch v phc v tt hoc cht lng dy hc tt  con em h pht trin tt hn.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	- Cht lng gio dc  cc trng cng lp cao hn so vi cc trng ngoi cng lp v vy cha m hc sinh c xu hng bng mi cch lo cho con vo trng cng.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	- Tm l khoa c, mong mun cho con em c hc  mi trng gio dc tt, an ton, hiu qu, c thy, c gii dn n vic chy trng, chy lp.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	- Hc ph ca mt s trng ngoi cng lp c cht lng thu cao nn mt s gia nh khng c iu kin cho con theo hc nn bng mi cch lo cho con em vo trng cng.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	c) Gii php<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	 tng bc hn ch v tin ti chm dt tnh trng &ldquo;chy trng&rdquo;, &ldquo;chy lp&rdquo;, B GD T ch o cc c s gio dc thc hin cc gii php sau:<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	(1) To mi trng gio dc thn thin, hiu qu thu ht c hc sinh n hc tp.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	(2) u t c s vt cht, trang thit b dy hc m bo phc v hiu qu cho vic nng cao cht lng gio dc ton din, hiu qu;<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	(3) Tng cng kim tra, gim st vic tuyn sinh ng quy ch ca B.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	(4) i mi vic thi, kim tra, nh gi i vi hc sinh  gim p lc thi c.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	(5) Tng cng tuyn truyn i vi cha m hc sinh, ton x hi gt b tm l khoa c.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	(6) Ch o cc a phng tng cng qun l cht lng gio dc trong cc trng mm non, ph thng ngoi cng lp, thu hp khong cch v cht lng gio dc gia trng cng lp v ngoi cng lp, gia cc trng trn a bn.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	<strong>6. Vn  dy thm, hc thm</strong><br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	 qun l dy thm, hc thm, ngy 31/01/2007, B Gio dc v o to  ban hnh Quyt nh s 03/2007/Q-BGDT quy nh v dy thm, hc thm, trong  quy nh y ban nhn dn cp tnh v U ban nhn dn cp huyn chu trch nhim qun l dy thm hc thm trn a bn.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	n nay, hu ht cc S Gio dc v o to  tham mu cho U ban nhn dn cp tnh ban hnh quy nh v t chc dy thm, hc thm trn a bn, ng thi  ban hnh cc vn bn hng dn thc hin. Tuy nhin, trn thc t, ti mt s tnh, thnh ph, hin tng dy thm, hc thm trn lan vn cha c khc phc c hiu qu. Thc trng ny xut pht t nhng nguyn nhn c bn sau:<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	- Vic qun l dy thm, hc thm ca cc c s gio dc  mt s a phng cn lng lo, cha nghim.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	- Mt s gio vin cn c t tng v li trong vic dy thm, hc thm.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	- Cng tc kim tra, gim st ca c quan qun l nh nc v gio dc v o to (B Gio dc v o to, y ban nhn dn v S Gio dc v o to cc tnh, thnh ph) i vi vic thc hin Quyt nh s 03/2007/Q-BGDT v dy thm, hc thm cha thng xuyn, hiu qu.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	- Cc vi phm v dy thm, hc thm trn lan cha c x l kp thi, nghim minh.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	 hn ch, i n chm dt vic dy thm, hc thm trn lan v thc hin nghim Quyt nh s 03/2007/Q-BGDT, B Gio dc v o to  v ang tin hnh cc gii php sau y:<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	- Tng cng cng tc tuyn truyn, to s ng thun trong nhn dn v ph huynh hc sinh v cc ch trng ca ngnh, ca a phng v qun l dy thm, hc thm.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	- Ch ng bn bc, trao i, phi hp vi U ban nhn dn cc tnh, thnh ph ch o cc cp qun l, cc ngnh chc nng  cao vai tr, trch nhim qun l ca Hiu trng, gio vin ch nhim; m rng cng tc tham gia gim st ca cc on th  a phng v trong nh trng, ca Hi cha m hc sinh i vi vic dy thm, hc thm, ng thi tng cng cng tc thanh tra, kim tra, x l nghim khc, kp thi cc sai phm trong vic thc hin cc quy nh v dy thm, hc thm.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	- Tip tc ch o dy hc 2 bui/ngy i vi cc trng ph thng (theo cng vn s 7291/BGDT-GDTrH ngy 01/11/2010 ca B Gio dc v o to) vi mc ch thc hin mc tiu gio dc ton din, gp phn nng cao cht lng gio dc; p ng nhu cu ca gia nh v x hi trong vic qun l, gio dc hc sinh.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	- Ch o thc hin hng dn iu chnh ni dung dy hc gio dc ph thng theo hng tinh gim (theo cng vn 5842/BGDT-VP ngy 01/9/2011 ca B Gio dc v o to), dnh thi lng  cng c, h thng ha kin thc  hc cho hc sinh, ph o ti lp i vi hc sinh c hc lc yu km.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	- Tip tc ch o thc hin i mi phng php dy hc, i mi kim tra, nh gi, ci tin cc cng tc thi theo chun kin thc, k nng, gim p lc v kim tra, thi c cho hc sinh.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	- Tip tc nghin cu,  xut ch  chnh sch ci thin i sng ca gio vin.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	- V lu di, xy dng l trnh thc hin i mi cn bn, ton din ni dung, chng trnh, phng php dy hc, thi c theo tinh thn Ngh quyt i hi ln th XI ca ng.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	<strong>7. Vn  thu, chi u nm hc</strong><br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	Theo phn cp qun l, y ban nhn dn cc tnh, thnh ph chu trch nhim trc Chnh ph v pht trin gio dc, thc hin chc nng qun l nh nc v gio dc trn a bn tnh, trong  c nhim v qun l, kim tra vic s dng ngn sch nh nc chi cho gio dc theo quy nh ca Lut Ngn sch nh nc v phn cp qun l ngn sch hin hnh; c nhim v qun l vic thu, chi hc ph, l ph v cc khon thu hp php khc ca cc c s gio dc v huy ng cc ngun lc  pht trin gio dc a phng.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	Vi trch nhim l c quan qun l nh nc v gio dc, B Gio dc v o to  ban hnh, phi hp vi cc B, ngnh ban hnh cc vn bn quy phm php lut, ch ng phi hp vi cc a phng trong vic qun l, hng dn, kim tra vic s dng ngn sch nh nc v cc khon thu hp php khc i vi cc c s gio dc; thc hin x hi ha gio dc, huy ng cc ngun lc x hi  pht trin gio dc; bo m quyn t ch, t chu trch nhim ca cc c s gio dc trc thuc theo quy nh ca php lut.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	Theo , hng nm, chun b cho nm hc mi, B Gio dc v o to u c vn bn gi S Gio dc v o to cc tnh, thnh ph hng dn cc nhim v cn trin khai, trong  c nhim v tham mu vi y ban nhn dn cp tnh ban hnh vn bn hng dn cc khon thu, chi ti cc c s gio dc trn a bn. ng thi, B cng c vn bn gi y ban nhn dn cc tnh, thnh ph  ngh phi hp, tng cng cc bin php chn chnh tnh trng lm thu trong cc c s gio dc.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	Vi s tham mu ca S Gio dc v o to, hu ht y ban nhn dn cc tnh, thnh ph  trnh v c Hi ng nhn dn cng cp ph duyt cc khon thu, mc hc ph, l ph v  hng dn cc c s gio dc trn a bn trin khai thc hin. Tuy nhin, trong thi gian qua, ti mt s c s gio dc (nht l  cc thnh ph ln) vn c tnh trng t  thu thm mt s khon tin ca ngi hc, s dng tin thu khng ng mc ch, khng tun th nhng yu cu v cng khai, minh bch trong thu chi, s dng cc hnh thc vn ng t nguyn nhng t chc thu tin bnh qun trn u hc sinh, gy bc xc cho cha m hc sinh v x hi.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	 gii quyt vic ny, ngy t u nm hc 2011-2012, lnh o B Gio dc v o to  lm vic trc tip vi lnh o y ban nhn dn v cc s, ban, ngnh lin quan ca thnh ph H Ni, thnh ph Hi Phng v thnh ph H Ch Minh  trao i, bn bc v thc trng v thng nht quan im, gii php nhm ngn chn v chm dt tnh trng lm thu ti cc thnh ph ny.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	B Gio dc v o to  thc hin thanh tra cng tc tuyn sinh u cp v cc khon thu u nm ti: Vnh Phc, Hi Dng, Lng Sn, H Ni, Hi Phng; ang ch o thanh tra ti thnh ph H Ch Minh v mt s a phng khc. Trn c s , cc on thanh tra  trao i rt kinh nghim vi cc a phng, ch o cc S Gio dc v o to chn chnh, x l kp thi nhng sai phm (nu c).<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	Thc t cho thy,  a phng no c s quan tm vo cuc quyt lit ca cp u, chnh quyn th ni  khng xy ra tnh trng lm thu, hoc nu  xy ra lm thu th cng nhanh chng c khc phc. V d: Ti  Nng,  x l k lut v iu chuyn cng tc i vi hiu trng v gio vin ch nhim c khuyt im trong vic vn ng quyn tin  trang b ti vi cho lp, nn tnh hnh cc nh trng lnh mnh r rt. Hoc  H Ni, lnh o thnh ph  giao ban vi lnh o cc qun, huyn, qun trit v kim tra cc nh trng trong vic thu, chi u nm hc, do vy nhiu trng  tr li ph huynh cc khon thu sai quy nh.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	 tip tc chn chnh v chm dt tnh trng thu tri quy nh ca nh nc trong cc c s gio dc, B Gio dc v o to  v ang thc hin cc gii php:<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	- Ch o cc cp qun l gio dc tng cng kim tra, chn chnh v x l kp thi, nghim khc cc sai phm, trong , x l k lut nghim khc vi gio vin v hiu trng  cc c s gio dc cn  xy ra tnh trng lm thu v cc sai phm khc theo thm quyn v trch nhim qun l nh nc v gio dc  c quy nh ti Ngh nh s 115/2010/N-CP ngy 24/12/2010 ca Chnh ph.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	- Tng cng ch o, kim tra vic thc hin Quy ch cng khai i vi c s gio dc ca h thng gio dc quc dn (theo Thng t s 09/2009/TT-BGDT ngy 07/5/2009 ca B Gio dc v o to).<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	-  ngh U ban nhn dn cc cp quan tm b tr  kinh ph chi thng xuyn, m bo c cu ti a 80% chi lng v cc khon c tnh cht lng v ti thiu 20%  chi ging dy, hc tp v qun l nh trng theo quy nh.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	- D tho Thng t ban hnh iu l Ban i din cha m hc sinh (thay th iu l ban i din cha m hc sinh ban hnh theo Quyt nh s 11/2008/Q-BGDT ngy 28/3/2008), trong  s quy nh c th v r hn trch nhim, quyn hn ca Ban i din cha m hc sinh v cc khon thu m Ban i din cha m hc sinh khng c vn ng quyn gp ca ph huynh hc sinh. Hin nay, d tho Thng t ang c hon thin, d kin s ban hnh trong thng 12/2011.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	<strong>8. Vn  thiu trng mm non cng lp</strong><br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	Trong nm hc 2011-2012, c nc c 12.976 trng mm non, tng 265 trng so vi nm hc trc. Trong , trng cng lp: 9.742 trng, chim t l 75,1%; trng ngoi cng lp: 3.234 trng, chim t l 24,9%.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	Tng s phng hc cho Gio dc Mm non l 138.843, trong  c 65.629 phng hc kin c (chim t l 48%). Trong nm hc 2010 -2011, c nc  xy dng mi 10.746 phng hc, 3.684 cng trnh nc sch v 10.202 b, h v sinh.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	Mc d s lng phng hc cho Gio dc Mm non  tng ln ng k, nhng vn thiu trm trng; C nc hin vn thiu 26.886 phng hc (tnh theo quy nh s lng tr em/lp ca iu l trng mm non), 34.104 nh v sinh.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	Thiu phng hc l nguyn nhn ch yu dn n tnh trng qu ti  cc trng mm non ti cc thnh ph,  th ln, c bit l th  H Ni v thnh ph H Ch Minh. Bn cnh , s chnh lch kh ln v hc ph, cht lng gio vin, c s vt cht gia trng mm non cng lp v t thc cng l nguyn nhn dn n tnh trng qu ti cho cc trng cng lp.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	 gii quyt tnh trng thiu trng, lp v tnh trng qu ti  cc trng mm non ti cc thnh ph,  th ln, B Gio dc v o to phi hp vi cc a phng  v ang tp trung ch o thc hin mt s vn  sau:<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	- Tch cc tham mu Chnh ph ban hnh c ch chnh sch pht trin gio dc mm non, ph hp vi s pht trin kinh t x hi ca tng giai on. ng thi, B Gio dc v o to cng  ch ng ban hnh cc vn bn quy phm php lut nhm tng cng cng tc qun l nh nc v gio dc mm non.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	- Ch o v hng dn cc S gio dc v o to cc tnh, thnh ph tham mu vi y ban nhn dn cc cp tng cng r sot, quy hoch mng li, quy m trng, lp; dnh din tch xy dng trng mm non khi ph duyt thnh lp cc khu dn c mi, khu  th, khu ch xut, khu cng nghip; thc y tin  xy dng cc trng cng lp  nhng phng, x cha c trng mm non; u t, ci to, nng cp c s vt cht cho cc trng cng lp ang xung cp. y mnh x hi ha, a dng ha cc loi hnh trng, lp mm non, to iu kin v c ch, chnh sch cho cc t chc, c nhn thnh lp trng mm non ngoi cng lp  nhng ni iu kin kinh t x hi pht trin.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	- Tng cng tuyn truyn, ph bin kin thc cho cc bc cha m c con trong la tui mm non,  h c th nui dy con tt ti gia nh, gp phn gim ti cho cc nh trng.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	- Ch o cc a phng tng cng qun l cht lng chm sc, nui dng, gio dc tr trong cc trng mm non ngoi cng lp, thu hp khong cch v cht lng chm sc, nui dng, gio dc tr gia trng mm non cng lp v ngoi cng lp. Thc hin cng khai v ti chnh, cng khai cng tc tuyn sinh, cng khai v iu kin i ng gio vin, c s vt cht ca nh trng,  ngi dn c th la chn cc c s gio dc mm non ph hp vi iu kin ca gia nh v gim st c hot ng ca nh trng.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	<strong>9. V gii php  nng cao cht lng gio dc  cc tnh min ni </strong><br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	T nhiu nm nay, B Gio dc v o to  ch tr, phi hp vi cc b, ngnh tham mu  ng v Nh nc ban hnh nhiu chnh sch h tr  vng min ni, vng ng bo dn tc v ch o cc a phng thc hin nhm gp phn nng cao cht lng gio dc nh:  n Kin c ha trng, lp hc v nh cng v cho gio vin giai on 2008-2012,  n Cng c v pht trin h thng trng ph thng dn tc ni tr giai on 2011-2015(Quyt nh s 1640/Q-TTg ngy 20/9/2011 ca Th tng Chnh ph), vi mc tiu tng cng u t xy dng  mi tnh c t nht 1 trng Ph thng dn tc ni tr cp tnh v mt s trng ph thng dn tc ni tr cp huyn, trng ph thng dn tc bn tr nhm thu ht c tt c tr trong  tui n trng; Quyt nh ban hnh mt s chnh sch h tr hc sinh bn tr v trng ph thng dn tc bn tr, cc chnh sch u tin cho pht trin gio dc dn tc(Quyt nh s 85/2010/Q-TTg ngy 21/12/2010); Ngh nh s 82/2010/N-CP ngy 15/7/2010 ca Th tng Chnh ph quy nh vic dy v hc ting ni, ch vit ca dn tc thiu s trong cc c s gio dc ph thng v trung tm gio dc thng xuyn; Quyt nh s 2123/Q-TTg ngy 22/11/2010 ca Th tng Chnh ph ph duyt  n Pht trin gio dc i vi cc dn tc rt t ngi giai on 2010-2015; Thc hin cng bng trong x hi v mt s chnh sch min, gim hc ph, cp hc bng, cho vay i hc.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	B Gio dc v o to cng  ch o nhiu nhm gii php nh tng thi lng dy ting Vit, s dng ti liu cng ngh gio dc, dy hc song ng da trn ting m , nhn vin h tr gio vin, xy dng mi trng s dng ting Vit trong dy hc v hot ng tp th&hellip;<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	Vi nhng gii php trn, gio dc  vng ng bo cc dn tc thiu s, vng su, vng xa tng bc pht trin: S lng hc sinh hc  cc trng ph thng dn tc ni tr, ph thng dn tc bn tr tng ln; hu ht cc em hc sinh dn tc ni tr c phm cht o c tt, gi gn c bn sc vn ha ca dn tc mnh, ng thi tip thu cc nt p vn ha ng x vn minh, tin tin thng qua cc hot ng ca nh trng; cht lng dy v hc  cc tnh min ni v dn tc ngy cng c ci thin. Tuy nhin, do xut pht im thp nn cht lng gio dc cha ngang bng vi vng thun li.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	 tng bc nng cao cht lng gio dc min ni, vng dn tc, B Gio dc v o to xc nh nhng nhim v trng tm v gii php ln nh sau:<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	- Nhim v trng tm: Pht trin gio dc  vng su, vng xa, vng kh khn, vng dn tc, bo m cng bng x hi trong gio dc; Thc hin tt cc chnh sch u i, h tr i vi hc sinh dn tc thiu s, gio vin cng tc  vng c bit kh khn, vng dn tc; Nng cao cht lng gio dc vng dn tc thiu s.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	- Mt s gii php:<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	+ Tng cng u t c s vt cht, thit b cho cc trng ph thng v trng ph thng dn tc ni tr, ph thng dn tc bn tr theo hng ng b, hin i.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	+ Thc hin tt chnh sch u i, chnh sch tn dng sinh vin, h tr i vi hc sinh, sinh vin ngi dn tc thiu s  nhng vng kh khn; Tip tc thc hin "3 " i vi mi hc sinh.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	+ Chm lo cng tc o to, bi dng nng cao nng lc cho cn b qun l v gio vin m bo cht lng,  v s lng, ng b v c cu, tng dn t l gio vin ngi dn tc, ngi a phng; Thc hin tt cc ch  chnh sch cho gio vin, ngi hc vng dn tc, min ni; C chnh sch tha ng thu ht nh gio n lm vic c vng dn tc thiu s, vng su, vng xa; Ch o vic dy ting dn tc thiu s cho cn b, cng chc, gio vin cng tc  vng dn tc thiu s; Bo m  nh cng v cho nh gio.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	+ Ch trng ch o i mi phng php dy hc, i mi kim tra nh gi  nng cao cht lng dy v hc; Thc hin c hiu qu vic dy hc ting dn tc thiu s.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	+ Cung cp min ph hoc gim gi sch gio khoa, hc phm,  dng hc tp cho hc sinh vng kh khn, vng dn tc thiu s v cc i tng chnh sch x hi.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	+ B Gio dc v o to  thng nht vi Hi ng Dn tc ca Quc hi, cng cc c quan hu quan nghin cu  xut chnh sch i vi gio dc dn tc cho ph hp tnh hnh mi, trn tinh thn qun trit Ngh quyt i hi ng ton quc ln th XI.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: right;">\r\n	<strong>B GD&T</strong></p>', '', 1, 5, 0, 31, '2011-12-13 07:54:03', 62, '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-12-13 07:52:55', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', '', 1, 0, 2, '', '', 0, 1, '');
