(63, 'Thi HSG quc gia nm 2012 s c mt s im mi', 'thi-hsg-quc-gia-nm-2012-s-co-mt-s-im-mi', '', '<p>\r\n	<strong>B GD&T va ban hnh hng dn t chc k thi chn HSG quc gia THPT nm 2012. </strong></p>\r\n<table align="center" width="100%">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n				<p class="storyInlinePhoto">\r\n					<img src="http://giaoducthoidai.vn/dataimages/201112/original/images605057_1.jpg" width="95%" /></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>\r\n	Theo hng dn ny, t nm 2012, cng vi vic thc hin hnh thc thi vit v thi lp trnh trn my vi tnh, B GD&T s tng bc trin khai thc hin hnh thc thi ni i vi cc mn Ngoi ng v hnh thc thi thc hnh i vi cc mn Vt l, Ha hc, Sinh hc. Bc u, trong k thi HSG nm 2012, cc mn Ngoi ng s c thm hnh thc thi ni  mc c thoi ca th sinh; i vi cc mn Vt l, Ha hc, Sinh hc, s c cu hi v thc hnh trong  thi.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	Phm vi ni dung thi s nm chng trnh gio dc THPT hin hnh v chng trnh chuyn su cc mn chuyn cp THPT. Thi gian thi trong hai ngy 11 v 12/1/2012.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	B GD&T cng cng b quy nh ring i vi thi ni mn Ngoi ng, trong  c quy trnh thc hin phn thi ca th sinh.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	C th, sau khi vo phng thi, th sinh bc thm  thi, nhn giy nhp t gim th trong phng thi, s dng tn truy cp v mt khu do gim th trong phng thi cp  ng nhp vo trang thi. ng nhp thnh cng vo trang thi, th sinh s kch chut vo  &ldquo;Vo thi&rdquo;  hin th ca s bi thi. Sau , th sinh phi ngay lp tc kch chut tri vo  &ldquo;Allow&rdquo; (nu khng bi thi ca th sinh s b v hiu), ri chun b cu tr li cho cu hi trong bi thi. Th sinh s bt u tr li khi h thng bo bt u ghi m.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	H thng s t ng ngng ghi m khi ht thi gian tr li cho php. Khi trn mn hnh my hin th ch &ldquo; gi ln server. Bn  hon thnh tr li cu hi&rdquo;, th sinh kch chut vo  &ldquo;ti v&rdquo;  lu file ghi m vo th mc do gim th to sn, tip theo kch vo  &ldquo;np bi&rdquo;  kt thc phn thi; sau , kch chut tri vo  &ldquo;thot&rdquo;  thot ra khi ti khon thi. Cui cng, th sinh cng gim th trong phng thi kim tra file ghi m  lu trn my tnh v k xc nhn ln a CD ghi file .<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	Lu , khi h thng bt u ghi m, th sinh phi c m s ca  thi, ni dung cu cu hi trong  thi trc khi bt u tr li, trng hp ngc li, phn tr li ca th sinh b coi l phm quy. Th sinh khng c  cp n cc thng tin c nhn trong phn tr li, khng c to ra cc ting ng nhm nh du phn thi ca mnh. Gim th trong phng thi cng khng c to ra ting ng l khi h thng ang ghi m phn tr li ca th sinh.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: right;">\r\n	<strong>GD&T</strong></p>', '', 1, 0, 0, 0, '2011-12-13 07:58:38', 62, '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-12-13 07:58:02', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', '', 1, 0, 3, '', '', 0, 0, ''),
