(65, 'Hng ti mt trit l dy vn', 'hng-ti-mt-trit-ly-dy-vn', '', '<p class="pHead" style="text-align: justify;">\r\n	TTCT - Dy vn gp phn tch cc nht, hiu qu nht v su sc trong qu trnh hnh thnh nhn cch con ngi...</p>\r\n<p class="pBody" style="text-align: justify;">\r\n	C mt giai thoi xa th v k v mt k thi v tranh theo ch  &ldquo;trng&rdquo;: c hai tc phm ng lu  v c vn . Bc tranh th nht v mt trng trn vnh vnh, r rng; bc th hai khng thy trng u c, ch c m my rc sng.</p>\r\n<p class="pBody" style="text-align: justify;">\r\n	Gim kho A chm bc th nht im 10; bc th hai im 0 (v lc ). Gim kho B chm bc th nht 5 im (im trung bnh); bc th hai 10 im (im tuyt i) v gii thch y mi l bc tranh ngh thut ch thc, y sng to, c v theo th php &ldquo;dng vn ha nguyt&rdquo; (ly my v trng).</p>\r\n<p class="pBody" style="text-align: justify;">\r\n	D nhin chm thi th phi c p n. Nhng ch bit c p n m qun mt thc t bi lm ca th sinh th c khc g ngi i sa giy ch tin vo ci ni chn ca mnh! Hung chi &ldquo;ci ni&rdquo; d l l tng my cng ch l mt kiu ging Procuste m thi (trong thn thoi phng Ty, nhn vt Procuste c mt ci ging; khi bt c ai Procuste o ngi  bng ci ging ca mnh.</p>\r\n<p class="pBody" style="text-align: justify;">\r\n	Ai va vn th c tha; ai qu kh th cht bt; ai ngn hn th b ko ra)! T thc t chm thi, ti cm thy lo lng t nhiu chng ta vn dng p n nh mt kiu ging Procuste.</p>\r\n<p class="pBody" style="text-align: justify;">\r\n	Bao lu nay, chng ta tri buc mnh mt cch nghit ng trong nhng yu cu c tnh nguyn tc v cht php lnh: gio n, p n, t l hc sinh ln lp, hc sinh thi u, t l hc sinh gii... Qun quanh v lng tng trong nhng chic vng kim c y v chng ta khng c mt trit l dy vn.</p>\r\n<p class="pBody" style="text-align: justify;">\r\n	Cn thit c mt trit l gio dc hon chnh  hnh thnh mt trit l dy vn thch ng. Trong lch s gio dc ca th gii, tng c thi i mun o to nhng con ngi khng l, bch khoa, tng c thi mun o to nhng ngi qun t, nhng k trng phu. Nu nn gio dc VN hm nay mun o to nhng con ngi VN sng to  mi lnh vc th chng ta phi c mt trit l dy vn ng nh bn cht sng to ca loi hnh ny.</p>\r\n<p class="pBody" style="text-align: justify;">\r\n	Tim nng sng to ca hc sinh c nui dng, c kch thch, c to iu kin pht trin v th thch t nh n ln nh mt h thng s  ra nhng con ngi sng to. ng ngh tnh thm m v cht sng to ca vn hc ch kch thch, nui dng s sng to trong phm vi ngh thut. Hn ai ht, nhng nh khoa hc ln lun lun khng nh &ldquo;ngh thut v khoa hc l i cnh ca nhn loi&rdquo;.</p>\r\n<p class="pBody" style="text-align: justify;">\r\n	A. Einstein  tng tuyn b rng thuyt tng i ca ng c gi  t nhng trang tiu thuyt su thm ca Dostoievsky. V sau khi  tin s vt l, nh khoa hc v i v &ldquo;l i&rdquo; ny  n thm thy gio dy vn hi ng hc trung hc!</p>\r\n<p class="pBody" style="text-align: justify;">\r\n	Nu mun o to nhng con ngi sng to th chng ta phi c mt trit l dy vn dnh cho nhng ch th. iu ny phi ni Nht Bn l quc gia u tin  chu   lm c. Hin nay  hc ng VN, ngi thy c xu hng l nhng cng chc, cn hc sinh l nhng khch th. V vy, chng ta b qun tim nng sng to v tn ca ngi dy hc v ca hc sinh, sinh vin.</p>\r\n<p class="pBody" style="text-align: justify;">\r\n	Nhng trit l gio dc v trit l dy vn khng ch c nh th. Chng no x hi chng ta cn c nhng bc s la o bnh nhn, nhng thy thuc mn vic cha bnh  &ldquo;cht p&rdquo;, nhng quan chc tham ... chng ta vn cn suy ngh v trit l dy hc m nng nht l trit l dy vn.</p>\r\n<p class="pBody" style="text-align: justify;">\r\n	Chng no x hi chng ta cn c nhng hin tng ngi khim th phi ln ting &ldquo;ti l k khuyt tt, xin ng thu tin v xe but ca ti&rdquo;, chng ta vn cn phi b sung trit l dy vn. Chng no cn c nhng sinh vin ch v  khi tr s n 2 triu ng m ra tay git ngi bn gi cho mnh vay tin, chng ta vn cn lo ngh v mt trit l dy vn.</p>\r\n<p class="pBody" style="text-align: justify;">\r\n	Bi v vic dy vn gp phn tch cc nht, hiu qu nht v su sc trong qu trnh hnh thnh nhn cch con ngi.</p>\r\n<p class="pBody" style="text-align: right;">\r\n	<strong>Theo Tui tr online</strong></p>', '', 1, 0, 0, 0, '2011-12-13 08:00:52', 62, '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-12-13 08:00:11', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', '', 1, 0, 2, '', '', 0, 0, ''),
