(67, 'Lc thng tin du hc', 'lc-thong-tin-du-hc', '', '<p class="pHead" style="text-align: justify;">\r\n	TT - Hng lot trin lm du hc t cp ph thng n i hc, sau i hc c t chc. Gia mt rng thng tin du hc, hc sinh, sinh vin, ph huynh cn trang b mt s kinh nghim  tm ng thng tin du hc ang cn.</p>\r\n<table align="center" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="2" class="tLegend" style="BORDER-COLLAPSE: separate" width="40">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style="text-align: justify;">\r\n				<img border="1" class="lImage" hspace="0" src="http://images1.tuoitre.vn/tianyon/ImageView.aspx?ThumbnailID=529644" /></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style="text-align: justify;">\r\n				Theo cc nh t vn, ngi tham gia trin lm du hc cn tm hiu tht k thng tin du hc t i din tuyn sinh ca cc trng - nh: NH HNG</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p class="pBody" style="text-align: justify;">\r\n	Mt thc t nhiu hc sinh, sinh vin khi tham d trin lm du hc thng khng nm c thng tin v trng, loi hnh o to, ch  chnh sch vi du hc sinh quc t, iu kin n ... khin vic tm thng tin ti trin lm du hc nh &ldquo;ci nga xem hoa&rdquo;, ph cng sc, thi gian nhng khng t c kt qu.</p>\r\n<p class="pInterTitle" style="text-align: justify;">\r\n	Ch ng tm kim</p>\r\n<p class="pBody" style="text-align: justify;">\r\n	ng Nguyn Trng Giang, chuyn vin t vn Cng ty t vn du hc quc t CMI Vit Nam (Q.Tn Bnh, TP.HCM), chia s: &ldquo;Hc sinh, sinh vin d nh du hc ti quc gia no nn vo cc website ca lnh s qun, quc gia, trng...  nm ngay thng tin v nn gio dc ca nc , trong  cn ch  ti cc quy nh, chnh sch ca chnh ph i vi du hc sinh. Sau , phi ch ng tm hiu thng tin v ngnh ngh, trng, hc ph, iu kin n , lm thm... t cc ngun thng tin chnh thng hoc cc cng ty t vn du hc c uy tn, cht lng v c cc lnh s qun, cc c quan gio dc cng nhn&rdquo;.</p>\r\n<p class="pBody" style="text-align: justify;">\r\n	B Phm Th Thng Long, chuyn vin t vn Cng ty du hc Th H Mi (Q.1, TP.HCM), khuyn trc khi n d trin lm, ngi tham d nn xem k danh sch cc trng tham gia trin lm chun b sn danh sch cc trng mun gp. Ngoi ra, ngi tham d trin lm cn tm hiu xem bng cp, kinh nghim c cho php bn hi  iu kin nhp hc ca trng d nh du hc, v nn tham vn v s tng thch gia h thng vn bng  Vit Nam v quc gia chn du hc.</p>\r\n<p class="pBody" style="text-align: justify;">\r\n	Nhiu hc sinh, sinh vin coi cc trin lm du hc l dp  &ldquo;sn&rdquo; cc sut hc bng du hc bn phn, ton phn. L Anh, trng tuyn chng trnh hc bng Chnh ph Singapore, du hc sinh HQG Singapore, bt m: &ldquo;i din tuyn sinh ca cc trng khi t chc trin lm u c 1-2 sut hc bng bn phn hoc ton phn dnh cho hc sinh, sinh vin n tham d trin lm.  chp ly c hi ginh cc sut hc bng ny, hc sinh, sinh vin tham d cn chun b trc mt b h s bng ting Anh gm bi lun vit v bn thn, th gii thiu, bn thnh tch hc tp, cc giy chng nhn cc hot ng x hi...&rdquo;.</p>\r\n<p class="pInterTitle" style="text-align: justify;">\r\n	Hi ci mnh cn</p>\r\n<p class="pBody" style="text-align: justify;">\r\n	Khi n tham d trin lm du hc, vic lit k ra giy cc cu hi lin quan n vic chn trng, kha hc... sau  tng hp thnh mt danh sch cc cu hi l iu ngi tham d nn lm. L Th Mai Phng, cu du hc sinh Trng H Kent State (M), bt m: &ldquo;Ngi tham d thc mc vn  g hy ch ng, mnh dn hi i din tuyn sinh ca cc trng. Cu hi cng chi tit s gip bn hnh dung cuc sng du hc ca mnh  nc ngoi. Vo cui bui trin lm, bn c th n tr chuyn thn mt vi i din tuyn sinh ca cc trng  trao i thm cc thng tin khc v cuc sng, con ngi...  quc gia d nh i du hc&rdquo;.</p>\r\n<p class="pBody" style="text-align: justify;">\r\n	Theo anh Nguyn Thi, chuyn vin t vn Cng ty du hc Vietint (Q.1), hc sinh, sinh vin, ph huynh n d trin lm khng nn ly tt c cc ti liu c sn trn quy, m ch nn thu thp nhng thng tin thch hp. Khi chn c trng ng k i du hc, ngi tham d ch nn thu thp tt c cc thng tin lin quan n trng d nh du hc. Ngoi ra, nu s trng bn chn vt qu hai, bn cn so snh v hc ph, chng trnh o to, iu kin n , xp hng trng...  tm hiu thng tin.</p>\r\n<p class="pBody" style="text-align: justify;">\r\n	Khi i du hc t tc, khu chng minh ti chnh l cc k quan trng. Nu hc sinh, sinh vin khng chng minh c bn thn c kh nng t tc ti chnh gm: hc ph, n , sinh hot, mua sch v, di chuyn... s b nh rt visa ngay. V th ch Phm Th Dung, chuyn vin t vn Cng ty t vn du hc L&V (Q.3), cho bit: &ldquo;Khi trao i vi i din tuyn sinh ca cc trng, bn cn trnh by c th, r rng v iu kin ti chnh, nhng kh khn, vng mc v tnh hnh ti chnh ca bn thn, gia nh  nhn c nhng li khuyn ng nht&rdquo;.</p>\r\n<p class="pInterTitle" style="text-align: justify;">\r\n	Tnh to trc hc bng bn phn</p>\r\n<p class="pBody" style="text-align: justify;">\r\n	Vic cc trng t chc trin lm thng bo trao tng cc sut hc bng bn phn t 20-90% hc ph ch l chiu  thuyt phc bn quyt nh i du hc. Khi du hc ti nc ngoi, hc ph ch l mt phn nh, chi ph sinh hot, n , i li, mua sch v, bo him... mi l iu ng lo ngi. V vy, khi bt ng nhn c cc sut hc bng ny, ngi tham d cn tnh to, phi tm hiu k cc khon chi ph ngoi hc ph, nu vt qu kh nng ca gia nh, bn thn th nn t b  tm kim cc c hi khc.</p>\r\n<p class="pBody" style="text-align: justify;">\r\n	<strong>(S/T)</strong></p>', '', 1, 0, 0, 0, '2011-12-13 08:03:50', 62, '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-12-13 08:03:12', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', '', 1, 0, 1, '', '', 0, 0, ''),
