(69, 'Thi tt nghip THPT: B thi cm, chm cho t 2012', 'thi-tt-nghip-thpt-b-thi-cm-chm-cheo-t-2012', '', '<p class="summary" style="text-align: justify;">\r\n	B GDT s giao quyn ch ng cho Gim c S GDT a phng quyt nh vic thnh lp cc hi ng coi thi, chm thi.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">\r\n	Ngy 12.12, B GDT cng b d tho Thng t v vic sa i b sung mt s iu ca quy ch thi tt nghip THPT.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">\r\n	Theo , bt u t k thi tt nghip THPT nm 2012, B s chnh thc b hnh thc thi theo cm v chm cho bi thi t lun gia cc trng. Thay vo , B s giao quyn ch ng cho Gim c S GDT a phng quyt nh vic thnh lp cc hi ng coi thi, chm thi, mi hi ng gm mt hoc nhiu trng ph thng, mi mn t lun c 2 t chm thi, m bo gio vin khng chm bi thi t lun ca hc sinh trng mnh ging dy. Cc hi ng coi thi bn giao trc tip cho hi ng chm thi khng qua s GDT.</p>\r\n<table align="center" width="100%">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n				<div>\r\n					<p class="storyInlinePhoto" style="text-align: justify;">\r\n						<img src="http://images.danviet.vn/CMSImage/Resources/Uploaded/baogiay2/297_11_hoc-sinh-THPT.jpg" width="95%" /></p>\r\n				</div>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n				<div style="text-align: justify;">\r\n					Thi tt nghip THPT s khng cn thi cm, chm cho.</div>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">\r\n	Ngoi ra, B cng b thanh tra y quyn ca B trong k thi, gim c cc s t thnh lp cc on thanh tra, trong  c th tng cng cn b, ging vin cc trng H, C lm cng tc coi thi.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">\r\n	Vic lp danh sch th sinh ng k thi cng c sa i, b sung. C th: Trong mi hi ng coi thi, danh sch th sinh c sp xp theo 3 bc.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">\r\n	Bc 1, xp theo th t ban: Th sinh Ban Khoa hc t nhin, Ban Khoa hc x hi v nhn vn, Ban C bn; th sinh gio dc thng xuyn (nu c).</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">\r\n	Bc 2, xp theo th t u tin ca mn thi ngoi ng (tr th sinh gio dc thng xuyn): Ting Anh, ting Nga, ting Php, ting Trung Quc, ting c, ting Nht.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">\r\n	Bc 3, lp danh sch th sinh cho mi mn thi ngoi ng v dnh ring cho gio dc thng xuyn (nu c) theo th t a, b, c&hellip; ca tn th sinh. S bo danh ca th sinh c nh t 0001 n ht s th sinh ca hi ng coi thi.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">\r\n	Quy nh mi ca B GDT khng ch khin ph huynh hc sinh &ldquo;th pho&rdquo; m cn gip cc trng v s tho g nhiu kh khn. Hnh thc thi cm, chm cho c trin khai t nm 2009, theo  mi cm thi c t nht 3 trng hoc 3 trung tm gio dc thng xuyn.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">\r\n	Tin hnh c 3 nm, &ldquo;thi cm - chm cho&rdquo;  bc l nhng hn ch r rt gy kh khn rt ln i vi hc sinh vng su, vng xa. Tnh trng cc em phi vt ni bng rng hoc i nhiu cy s  n a im thi khin c th sinh v ph huynh mt mi. Bn cnh , mt s trng khng  iu kin vt cht  t chc thi theo cm cng kh &ldquo;loay hoay&rdquo;  trin khai hnh thc ny.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">\r\n	in hnh, s c &ldquo;11 tnh ng bng sng Cu Long cng nhau tha thun nng im trong k thi tt nghip nm 2011&rdquo;  cho thy s thiu khch quan trm trng ca hnh thc thi ny. Chnh v vy, theo nh gi ca cc chuyn gia gio dc &ldquo;hnh thc thi cm, chm cho sm mun cng&hellip; ph sn&rdquo;.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">\r\n	<strong>(Dn Vit)</strong></p>', '', 1, 4, 0, 21, '2011-12-13 08:05:17', 62, '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-12-13 08:04:31', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', '', 1, 0, 1, '', '', 0, 24, ''),
(70, 'Thnh cng hm nay, nn tng ngy mai', 'thanh-cong-hom-nay-nn-tng-ngay-mai', '', '<div id="detail-content">\r\n	<p style="text-align: justify;">\r\n		<strong>(GD&T) - Ngy 17/7, Hi ngh tng kt 4 nm thc hin Ch th s 33/2006/CT-TTg, s kt 3 nm phong tro thi ua &ldquo;Xy dng trng hc thn thin, hc sinh tch cc&rdquo; v tng kt nm hc 2010-2011, trin khai nhim v nm hc 2011-2012 ti Cao Lnh, tnh ng Thp tip tc ngy lm vic th hai v  kt thc thnh cng tt p. </strong></p>\r\n	<table align="center" cellpadding="3" cellspacing="0" class="image center" width="550">\r\n		<tbody>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td>\r\n					<img alt="Cc lnh o S k cam kt thi ua" height="334" src="http://www.gdtd.vn/dataimages/201107/original/images549580_1.jpg" width="550" /></td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td align="center" class="image_desc">\r\n					Cc lnh o S k cam kt thi ua</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n		</tbody>\r\n	</table>\r\n	<p style="text-align: justify;">\r\n		Trong ngy hm nay, hi ngh tip tc nhn c nhiu tham lun,  kin ng gp, chia s kinh nghim ca cc i biu. Trong  ng ch  l tham lun ca ng Trng Kim Minh, Gim c S GD&T tnh Lo Cai; ng Nguyn nh Ban, Hiu trng Trng THCS Phan Chu Trinh, tnh k Lk v nhng chuyn bin vt bc ca c s sau 4 nm thc hin ch th s 33/2006/CT-TTg v 3 nm trin khai phong tro thi ua &ldquo;Xy dng trng hc thn thin, hc sinh tch cc&rdquo;. Cc tham lun u nhn mnh: hiu qu r nht m cuc vn ng &ldquo;Hai khng&rdquo; v phong tro thi ua &ldquo;Xy dng trng hc thn thin, hc sinh tch cc&rdquo; mang ti  l vic c x hi cng chm lo cho gio dc v o to. C h thng chnh tr vo cuc, s ng lng ca nhn dn. V  l c s  gio dc a phng chuyn bin tch cc theo hng thc cht, tng bc nng cao cht lng. V  ngha tch cc cng nh hiu qu ca cuc vn ng Hai khng v phong tro thi ua Xy dng trng hc thn thin, hc sinh tch cc&rdquo;, ton ngnh cn tip tc duy tr v pht trin trong thi gian ti. (Xem thm chi tit  kin cc i biu v vic thc hin ch th s 33/2006/CT-TTg v phong tro &ldquo;Xy dng trng hc thn thin, hc sinh tch cc&rdquo; )</p>\r\n	<p style="text-align: justify;">\r\n		Cng trong ngy hm nay, B GD&T  t chc tuyn dng khen thng nhng c nhn, tp th t thnh tch xut sc trong nm hc 2010-2011.</p>\r\n	<table align="center" cellpadding="3" cellspacing="0" class="image center" width="550">\r\n		<tbody>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td>\r\n					<img alt="Ph Th tng Nguyn Thin Nhn pht biu ch o ti hi ngh" height="413" src="http://www.gdtd.vn/dataimages/201107/original/images549557_2.JPG" width="550" /></td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td align="center" class="image_desc">\r\n					Ph Th tng Nguyn Thin Nhn pht biu ch o ti hi ngh</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n		</tbody>\r\n	</table>\r\n	<p style="text-align: justify;">\r\n		nh gi v nhng thnh tu sau mt nm hc, ng thi nhn li 4 nm trin khai cuc vn ng &ldquo;Hai khng&rdquo;, 3 nm trin khai phong tro thi ua &ldquo;Xy dng trng hc thn thin, hc sinh tch cc&rdquo; , y vin trung ng ng, Ph Th tng Chnh ph Nguyn Thin Nhn  ghi nhn v nh gi cao nhng n lc ca ton ngnh trong vic quyt lit chng tiu cc, yu km trong ngnh, tng bc nng cao cht lng gio dc theo hng thc cht v c chiu su. Ph Th tng nhn mnh: Ngnh gio dc cn phi tip tc khng ngng i mi, nng cao cht lng gio dc, thc hin mt cch trit  v thit thc cc phong tro thi ua, to ng lc phn u rn luyn cao hn na, mnh m hn na trong gio vin v hc sinh. Ton ngnh cn qun trit ch o ca Th tng Chnh ph Nguyn Tn Dng v su nhim v trng tm.  l i mi cng tc qun l gio dc, nng cao cht lng dy v hc; i mi v gim ti chng trnh gio dc ph thng; Chm lo cho i sng gio vin v tch cc xy dng i ng cn b qun l, nh gio; Nng cao cht lng dy v hc ngoi ng, tip tc u t v nng cao c s vt cht trng lp; Nhanh chng xy dng chin lc pht trin gio dc giai on 2011-2020.  vic i mi tt v hiu qu, ngnh gio dc v cc a phng cn phi xy dng c mi trng gio dc s phm tt. Trong qu trnh i mi phi bm st thc tin, lng nghe  kin t c s  cng cuc i mi mang tnh bn vng hn. Nm hc mi 2011-2012, ngnh gio dc cng phi nng cao trch nhim i vi x hi; Quyt lit thc hin i mi ton din, trong  i mi qun l l hng t ph. c bit, gio dc ph thng khng ch ch trng vic dy kin thc m cn phi tch hp vic dy kin thc vi dy k nng cho hc sinh theo hng tng cng nng lc cng dn trn bc ng hi nhp.</p>\r\n	<table align="center" cellpadding="3" cellspacing="0" class="image center" width="500">\r\n		<tbody>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td>\r\n					<img alt="B trng Phm V Lun pht biu ti hi ngh" height="375" src="http://www.gdtd.vn/dataimages/201107/original/images549558_1.jpg" width="500" /></td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td align="center" class="image_desc">\r\n					B trng Phm V Lun kt lun hi ngh</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n		</tbody>\r\n	</table>\r\n	<p style="text-align: justify;">\r\n		Thay mt ton ngnh, B trng B GD&T Phm V Lun pht biu tip thu  kin ch o ca Ph Th tng. B trng khng nh: i vi Ch th 33/2006/CT-TTg, ngnh GD&T  ch ng trin khai,  c tinh thn trch nhim rt cao trc ng v nhn dn, li c thm s chia s chung tay ca cc b ngnh, lnh o cc a phng. Ngnh GD&T hin nay  bt kh khn hn 4 nm trc rt nhiu, n gi ny c th khng nh mc tiu c bn ca Ch th 33/2006/CT-TTg  c thc hin mt cch hiu qu. Trn c s pht huy nhng thnh tu  t c qua 4 nm thc hin Ch th s 33/2006/CT-TTg, 3 nm trin khai phong tro thi ua &ldquo;Xy dng trng hc thn thin, hc sinh tch cc&rdquo; cng nh thnh qu ca nm hc qua, ton ngnh cn quyt tm hn na, xy dng nn gio dc trung thc lnh mnh, cht lng. Nhng mi quan h c xc lp trong ni b ngnh gio dc, gia ngnh vi cc b ngnh khc  c xc lp trong qu trnh thc hin &ldquo;Hai khng&rdquo; v &ldquo;Xy dng trng hc thn thin, hc sinh tch cc&rdquo; s tip tc c duy tr v pht trin. Ton ngnh quyt tm khng  ti pht tiu cc  nhng ni  chng c tiu cc v kin quyt chng ti cng  nhng ni cn tiu cc.</p>\r\n	<table align="center" cellpadding="3" cellspacing="0" class="image center" width="550">\r\n		<tbody>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td>\r\n					<a href="http://gdtd.vn/dataimages/201107/original/images549739_1.jpg"><img alt="Ph Th tng Nguyn Thin Nhn trao bng khen cho cc tp th c thnh tch xut sc trong thc hin Ch th s 33/2006/CT-TTg" height="413" src="http://www.gdtd.vn/dataimages/201107/original/images549739_1.jpg" width="550" /></a></td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td align="center" class="image_desc">\r\n					Ph Th tng Nguyn Thin Nhn trao bng khen cho cc tp th c thnh tch xut sc trong thc hin Ch th s 33/2006/CT-TTg</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n		</tbody>\r\n	</table>\r\n	<p style="text-align: justify;">\r\n		Trong nhim v trin khai nm hc mi 2011-2012 ton ngnh phi i mi cn bn v ton din theo tinh thn Ngh quyt i hi ng ln th XI; ni dung i mi cn bn s c ngnh t chc nghin cu  c th ha v trin khai. Sp ti y, Chnh ph s c chng trnh hnh ng, cn s ng gp tr tu nhiu t ngnh GD&T, cc ngnh cc cp,  kin nhn dn. Trn c s ny, B s iu chnh ni dung i mi cho ph hp vi tnh hnh. Nm hc ny l nm hc u tin ca k hoch 5 nm nn c  ngha rt quan trng, cn phi c s quyt tm cao ca ton ngnh.</p>\r\n	<table align="center" cellpadding="3" cellspacing="0" class="image center" width="550">\r\n		<tbody>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td>\r\n					<img alt="B trng Phm V lun trao bng khen cho cc lnh o hon thnh xut sc nhim v nm hc" height="413" src="http://www.gdtd.vn/dataimages/201107/original/images549560_3.JPG" width="550" /></td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td align="center" class="image_desc">\r\n					B trng Phm V Lun trao bng khen cho cc n v hon thnh xut sc nhim v nm hc</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n		</tbody>\r\n	</table>\r\n	<p style="text-align: justify;">\r\n		Cng ti hi ngh, B trng lu  cc S GD&T mt s vn  mi. V thng t hng dn Ngh nh 115/2010/N-CP ngy 24/12/2010, B ang son tho, trong , c nhim v ca S GD&T qun l mt s trng C, H  a phng, B trng  ngh cc S GD&T nn tham mu vi UBND tnh  c th ch ng trong cc k hoch.V chng trnh CNTT trong i mi qun l, B ang c phn mm qun l v s trin khai rng trong tng lai, cc a phng c pht hin li g th phn nh v B, B s c hng dn v tho g. Ring vn  h tr SGK cho hc sinh ngho, va qua c thc t l c tnh h tr bng tin, nn b m hc sinh s dng vo vic khc. B trng  ngh cc gim c S quan tm iu chnh  &ldquo; khng  hc sinh no ngho phi b hc&rdquo; nh li Th tng Chnh ph  ch o.<br />\r\n		<strong> </strong></p>\r\n	<p style="text-align: justify;">\r\n		<strong><em>NH GI T C S:</em></strong></p>\r\n	<table align="right" cellpadding="3" cellspacing="0" class="image rightside" width="200">\r\n		<tbody>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td>\r\n					<img alt="ng ng Vn Hng, gim c S GD Bc Ninh" height="153" src="http://www.gdtd.vn/dataimages/201107/original/images549562_3.JPG" width="200" /></td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td align="center" class="image_desc">\r\n					ng ng Vn Hng, Gim c S GD&T Bc Ninh</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n		</tbody>\r\n	</table>\r\n	<p style="text-align: justify;">\r\n		<strong>*ng ng Vn Hng, Gim c S GD&T tnh Bc Ninh:</strong><br />\r\n		<strong>Cn tip tc duy tr, pht trin cc cuc vn ng v phong tro. </strong><br />\r\n		Hiu qu m cc cuc vn ng, phong tro mang li l rt r rng. V th, chng ta nn duy tr cc cuc vn ng v nhng phong tro thi ua nh hin nay, nhm thc y  thc t gic, tinh thn say m t hc, t sng to trong phng php ging dy ca gio vin v  thc hc tp ca hc sinh. Bi cc cuc vn ng, phong tro thi ua trn c cc cp, cc ngnh v nhn dn ng h rt cao.</p>\r\n	<p style="text-align: justify;">\r\n		Cuc vn ng &ldquo;Hai khng&rdquo; tht s mang li nhiu hiu qu tch cc cho ngnh gio dc. Sau 4 nm trin khai, cuc vn ng khng ch cho x hi thy trch nhim ca ton ngnh trong vic hng n gio dc thc cht, m cn ch ra cho x hi thy nhng im tch cc m ngnh gio dc ang c. Ngnh v cc a phng  c s ng thun, tinh thn dm thng thn nhn vo nhng hn ch, dm chp nhn cht lng gio dc thc cht (d t l i khi thp)  t  sa cha v tin b, gip cho x hi tin tng hn.</p>\r\n	<p style="text-align: justify;">\r\n		Tuy nhin, bn cnh nhng a phng thc hin tt, th cng cn khng t ni trong qu trnh thc hin vn cn mt s vn  t nhiu gp phi vng mc v hn ch. Mi cng vic u cn phi c qu trnh v s ng thun ng h ca mi cp chnh quyn. Trong , vai tr ca ngnh GD&T trong nh hng, h tr, tho g l rt quan trng.</p>\r\n	<table align="left" cellpadding="3" cellspacing="0" class="image leftside" width="200">\r\n		<tbody>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td>\r\n					<img alt="ng Nguyn Khc Ho, gim c S H Tnh" height="160" src="http://www.gdtd.vn/dataimages/201107/original/images549563_2.JPG" width="200" /></td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td align="center" class="image_desc">\r\n					ng Nguyn Khc Ho,Gim c S GD&T H Tnh</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n		</tbody>\r\n	</table>\r\n	<p style="text-align: justify;">\r\n		*<strong>ng Nguyn Khc Ho, Gim c S GD&T H Tnh: X hi cn c ci nhn khch quan v gio dc </strong><br />\r\n		Trin khai Ch th 33/2006/CT-TTg ca Chnh ph, cht lng gio dc  c ci thin qua tng nm. Sau 4 nm, tc ng ca &ldquo;Hai khng&rdquo; l rt r rng. Thi  coi thi, chm thi ca cn b, gio vin  nn np, nghim tc hn trc rt nhiu. Hin tng tiu cc trong thi c nh lm bi cho hc sinh, g bi cho hc sinh, cho hc sinh s dng ti liu&hellip; c ngn chn ht sc l kp thi.<br />\r\n		H Tnh chng ti khi thc hin cuc vn ng &ldquo;Hai khng&rdquo;  tng x l hng trm gio vin vi phm quy ch thi. C sau mi nm &ldquo;mnh tay&rdquo; nhng vi phm nh vy c ko gim i r rt. Thi c l mt p lc, nhng nu chng ta bit x l mt cch hi ha, bit lm cng tc tuyn truyn, gio dc, nng cao nhn thc mt cch hiu qu th kt qu mang li s thc cht.</p>\r\n	<p style="text-align: justify;">\r\n		C nhn ti thy &ldquo;Hai khng&rdquo; l rt cn thit. X hi cn c ci nhn khch quan v gio dc, ng thy t l  hi cao mt cht l t du hi nghi vn, ti thy  l vic ht sc bnh thng sau nhng g chng ta dm chp nhn i mt  sa i v i mi cng tc thi c, dy v hc. Cuc vn ng &ldquo;Hai khng&rdquo; rt c  ngha, ht sc cn thit v phi tip tc c thc hin. V nu khng c cuc vn ng &ldquo;Hai khng&rdquo; tnh th n  khc.</p>\r\n	<table align="left" cellpadding="3" cellspacing="0" class="image leftside" width="200">\r\n		<tbody>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td>\r\n					<img alt="ng Phan Hng, gim c S GD tnh k Lk" height="136" src="http://www.gdtd.vn/dataimages/201107/original/images549564_1.jpg" width="200" /></td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td align="center" class="image_desc">\r\n					ng Phan Hng, Gim c S GD&T k Lk</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n		</tbody>\r\n	</table>\r\n	<p style="text-align: justify;">\r\n		*<strong>ng Phan Hng, gim c S GD&T tnh k Lk</strong>: <strong>Hiu qu cho pht trin gio dc </strong><br />\r\n		Cuc vn ng &ldquo;Hai khng&rdquo;  mang li nhng chuyn bin ht sc r nt. D t l nm hc ny mt s tnh c s gia tng t bin nhng ti khng ngh  l kt qu c vn  m ti tin t l y v c bn l s tng trng mang tnh quy lut v s n lc ca ngnh, ca i ng thy c gio, ca hc sinh cng nh ca ton x hi. Trong gio dc vic pht trin tt nhin s vn cn nhng hn ch ny, tn ti kia cn phi khc phc. Nhng nhn vo ton cc ca ngnh gio dc th s chuyn bin y l iu ng mng.</p>\r\n	<p style="text-align: justify;">\r\n		Phong tro thi ua &lsquo;Xy dng trng hc thn thin, hc sinh tch cc&rdquo; l mt phong tro mang tnh ton din. Bi phong tro   cp n rt nhiu vn : nng cao cht lng gio dc, i mi phng php dy v hc, ri xy dng k nng sng cho hc sinh, gio dc truyn thng, o c&hellip;Chnh v th, lm tt phong tro thi ua ny, ngnh gio dc s c iu kin  pht trin mt cch bn vng. Sau 4 nm thc hin cuc vn ng &ldquo;Hai khng&rdquo; cng vi s chuyn bin chung ca c nc, th nhng chuyn bin trong ngnh gio dc tnh k Lk l ht sc r nt.</p>\r\n	<table align="right" cellpadding="3" cellspacing="0" class="image rightside" width="200">\r\n		<tbody>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td>\r\n					<img alt="G  S GD&T TR VINH" height="156" src="http://www.gdtd.vn/dataimages/201107/original/images549565_5.JPG" width="200" /></td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td align="center" class="image_desc">\r\n					ng Triu Vn Phn, Gim c S GD&T Tr Vinh</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n		</tbody>\r\n	</table>\r\n	<p style="text-align: justify;">\r\n		<strong>*ng Triu Vn Phn, Gim c S GD&T Tr Vinh:</strong> <strong>C x hi chm lo cho gio dc </strong><br />\r\n		iu ti tm c nht l cc cuc vn ng v phong tro ca ngnh  to ra  thc c x hi cng chm lo cho gio dc. Tr Vinh l tnh c 30% ng bo dn tc Khmer, i sng cn kh khn, do  vic hc sinh b hc ba nm trc l mt vn  nan gii. Qua phong tro, cc ngnh cc cp, c x hi cng chm lo cho hc sinh ngho. T  t l hc sinh b hc ko gim xung 1%. Ba nm qua vic kin c ha trng hc c quan tm cha tng c. Vic gii ngn vn tri phiu Chnh ph lun vt ch tiu, nm 2010 gii ngn ti 200%. Tc l ng vn mt nm  xy dng trc. C th ni phong tro Xy dng trng hc thn thin, hc sinh tch cc  to bc t ph v cht lng gio dc  Tr Vinh.</p>\r\n	<p style="text-align: justify;">\r\n		<strong>*ng V Vn Thng, Gim c S GD&T ng Thp:</strong> <strong>Khi dy s sng to t c s </strong><br />\r\n		Phong tro Trng hc thn thin, hc sinh tch cc  to ra lung sinh kh mi cho gio dc. Hc sinh thm yu ngi trng mnh, qu hng mnh, t tin vo chnh mnh  phn u tr thnh ngi hu ch. Vn  gio dc k nng sng c quan tm. n ng Thp c rt nhiu m hnh  c sng to t s s nh: t nhn dn khuyn hc, xut pht t huyn Cao Lnh  c nhn ra c tnh; M hnh hc sinh THCS Nguyn Th Lu lm hng dn vin di tch M c Nguyn Sinh Sc; Hay mt b m ngho ch c 1 cng t m nui 5 con hc xong i hc  th trn M Th. Ngay nh k thi tt nghip THPT va qua, mt hc sinh ngho i chn tru  huyn Thp Mi   th khoa k thi. Xy dng Trng hc thn thin, hc sinh tch cc  gip x hi quan tm n gio dc hn, hc sinh rn luyn k nng sng tt hn.</p>\r\n	<table align="left" cellpadding="3" cellspacing="0" class="image leftside" width="200">\r\n		<tbody>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td>\r\n					<a href="http://gdtd.vn/dataimages/201107/original/images549597_4.JPG"><img alt="ng L Hng Sn- Gim c S GD&T thnh ph H Ch Minh" height="169" src="http://www.gdtd.vn/dataimages/201107/original/images549597_4.JPG" width="200" /></a></td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td align="center" class="image_desc">\r\n					ng L Hng Sn, Gim c S GD&T thnh ph H Ch Minh</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n		</tbody>\r\n	</table>\r\n	<p style="text-align: justify;">\r\n		<strong>*ng L Hng Sn- Gim c S GD&T thnh ph H Ch Minh:</strong><br />\r\n		Hiu qu t c ln nht l to iu kin thun li cho hc sinh pht huy t duy, kh nng sng to, t hc ca mnh. Thy c gio dy hc chm cht theo tng c th, khng dy theo s ng hay theo t chng nh trc. Vic gio dc o c nhn cch, li sng, truyn thng cho cc em hc sinh c nhn rng. Thng qua cc tit hc, bi hc, kha hc lch s trong nh trng, chng ti quan tm b sung vo gio dc truyn thng lch s  a phng cng nh b tr t cc hot ng ngoi kha, dy k nng sng, nu nhng tm gng in hnh&hellip; gip cc em rn luyn o c nhn cch v li sng tt p&hellip;</p>\r\n	<p style="text-align: right;">\r\n		<br />\r\n		<br />\r\n		<strong>(GD&T)</strong></p>\r\n</div>', '', 1, 8, 0, 40, '2011-12-13 08:07:00', 62, '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-12-13 08:06:17', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', '', 1, 0, 1, '', '', 0, 9, ''),
(71, 'Thi tt nghip THPT 2012: Khng bt buc thi cm trng, xa chm cho', 'thi-tt-nghip-thpt-2012-khong-bt-buc-thi-cm-trng-xoa-chm-cheo', '', '<div style="text-align: justify;" class="fon33 mt1"><img style="float: left;" src="images/hinhanh/trangnhat/21839_0_35797.jpg" alt="alt" width="214" height="160" />K thi tt nghip THPT s khng cn bt buc t chc thi cm trng v chm cho gia cc tnh m thay vo  giao quyn ch ng cho gim c cc S GD-T. Bn cnh  b thanh tra y quyn ca B, a phng t thnh lp cc on thanh tra.</div>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"> l im quan trng trong d tho Thng t v vic sa i, b sung mt s iu ca quy ch thi tt nghip THPT m B GD-T ang ng ti xin  kin.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Cng theo d tho ny,  m bo cng tc coi thi cc a phng c th la chn cn b, ging vin tham gia thanh tra k thi trn a bn theo  ngh ca Ban ch o thi cp tnh.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Ngoi vic b thi cm, chm cho thng t d tho d kin m rng thnh phn tham gia lm th k v y vin Hi ng in sao  thi. C th: Th k v y vin Hi ng in sao  thi l chuyn vin ca S GD-T, cn b, gio vin, nhn vin ca cc trng ph thng. S lng th k v y vin do Gim c GD-T quy nh.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Gim c S GD-T ra quyt nh thnh lp Hi ng chm thi tt nghip ph thng trong , mi mn t lun c 2 t chm thi, m bo gio vin khng chm bi thi t lun ca hc sinh trng ph thng mnh ging dy.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Do thay i v phng thc t chc thi nn B GD-T cng  iu chnh nhng quy nh v phc kho bi thi. Theo , Hi ng phc kho c mt b phn lm phch bi thi t lun, c lp vi cc t chm thi. Hi ng phc kho c mt t chm trn my bi thi ca cc mn thi theo phng php trc nghim v b phn gim st trc tip, lin tc, thc hin nhim v theo hng dn chm thi trc nghim ca GD-T.<img style="float: right;" src="images/hinhanh/trangnhat/21839_0_35797.jpg" alt="alt" width="192" height="144" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">B GD-T cho bit, sau khi tip nhn  kin ng gp cc im sa i ny li tip tc c bn lun ti Hi ngh thi v tuyn sinh nm 2012. Sau khi thng nht cc  kin, trong thng 2/2012